code: private static Collection<Class<? extends Plugin>> addMockTransportIfMissing(Settings settings, Collection<Class<? extends Plugin>> plugins) {     boolean settingExists = NetworkModule.TRANSPORT_TYPE_SETTING.exists(settings).     String transportType = NetworkModule.TRANSPORT_TYPE_SETTING.get(settings).     if (settingExists == false || MockNioTransportPlugin.MOCK_NIO_TRANSPORT_NAME.equals(transportType)) {         if (plugins.contains(MockNioTransportPlugin.class)) {             return plugins.         } else {             plugins = new ArrayList<>(plugins).             plugins.add(MockNioTransportPlugin.class).             return plugins.         }     }     return plugins. }
